所有程序包的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • org.springframework.security.samples.config,
  • org.springframework.security.samples.data,
  • org.springframework.security.samples.mvc,
  • org.springframework.security.samples.mvc.config

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.web.context.AbstractContextLoaderInitializer (implements org.springframework.web.WebApplicationInitializer)
      • org.springframework.web.servlet.support.AbstractDispatcherServletInitializer
        • org.springframework.web.servlet.support.AbstractAnnotationConfigDispatcherServletInitializer
          • org.springframework.security.samples.config.MessageWebApplicationInitializer
    • org.springframework.security.samples.config.DataConfiguration
    • org.springframework.security.samples.mvc.DefaultController
    • org.springframework.security.samples.data.Message
    • org.springframework.security.samples.mvc.MessageController
    • org.springframework.security.samples.config.RootConfiguration
    • org.springframework.web.servlet.config.annotation.WebMvcConfigurerAdapter (implements org.springframework.web.servlet.config.annotation.WebMvcConfigurer)
      • org.springframework.security.samples.mvc.config.WebMvcConfiguration

接口分层结构

  • org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<T,ID>
    • org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<T,ID>
      • org.springframework.security.samples.data.MessageRepository
